creator: Anna Katharine Green
description:
LibriVox recording of The Defence of the Bride and Other Poems by Anna Katharine Green.
Read in English by Domenica Campbell; Ezwa; Crln Yldz Ksr; KHand; SionedV; Larry Wilson; reba; Newgatenovelist
Anna Katharine Green is now best-known for her popular mystery and detective stories, but she also wrote some excellent poetry. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
